<p>Apple released a slew of updates last week, and your two favorite geeks talk through all of them, answering your questions along the way. OS X 10.10.4, iOS 8.4, Apple Music, iTunes 12.2&#8230; you name it, John F. Braun and Dave Hamilton cover it. They even leave time for your questions to be answered, too!</p>
